			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Why tie it to a single expansion? 
<br />

<br />
While right now the elementals look like the "only" path to high-end play, comparable gear is available through LDoN and comparable and even better gear (including two different items with the "Time-level" pet focus) is available in GoD.
<br />

<br />
What is "broken" with the pet-focus approach that has been in the game for a long time?
<br />

<br />
Yes, the focii need to be more powerful and they need to be more accessible and have more steps (especially between DPoC and Minion of Eternity) but the <span style="font-style: italic">approach </span>itself seems completely sound.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.sovereignguild.org/forum/viewtopic.php?t=4429" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Itchyban of Veeshan</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
